<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fa" dir="rtl">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>کانال‌های ایلیا فارکس</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Vazirmatn:wght@400;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:"Vazirmatn",sans-serif;
}

body{
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#070707,#111,#050505);
min-height:100vh;
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
padding:20px;
overflow:hidden;
}

body::before{
content:"";
position:absolute;
width:350px;
height:350px;
background:#00ff88;
filter:blur(180px);
top:-100px;
right:-120px;
opacity:.25;
}

body::after{
content:"";
position:absolute;
width:350px;
height:350px;
background:#ffd700;
filter:blur(180px);
bottom:-100px;
left:-120px;
opacity:.18;
}

.box{
position:relative;
z-index:2;
width:100%;
max-width:430px;
background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);
backdrop-filter:blur(15px);
border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
border-radius:28px;
padding:35px 25px;
text-align:center;
box-shadow:0 0 40px rgba(0,0,0,.5);
animation:show .8s ease;
}

@keyframes show{
from{
opacity:0;
transform:translateY(30px);
}
to{
opacity:1;
transform:translateY(0);
}
}

h1{
color:#fff;
font-size:30px;
margin-bottom:12px;
font-weight:900;
}

p{
color:#bbb;
font-size:15px;
margin-bottom:30px;
}

.btn{
display:block;
width:100%;
text-decoration:none;
color:#fff;
padding:18px;
margin:15px 0;
border-radius:18px;
font-size:18px;
font-weight:700;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#00c853,#00ff88);
transition:.3s;
box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,255,136,.25);
}

.btn:hover{
transform:translateY(-5px) scale(1.03);
box-shadow:0 15px 35px rgba(0,255,136,.45);
}

.footer{
margin-top:30px;
color:#888;
font-size:13px;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="box">

<h1>📡 کانال‌های ایلیا فارکس</h1>

<p>برای ورود به کانال موردنظر روی دکمه مربوطه کلیک کنید.</p>

